{
  "stem": "18520.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 664.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, [INAUDIBLE] with guys, a head and a foot, and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's it-- goes in the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So but there was not crematorium, so they would put them in the-- in this-- they had ditches with the bulldozers, builded up.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the people with the wagons they used to carry the deaths out there and lay them out like herrings, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said, listen, I don't want him to die.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I get [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he didn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he is telling me, if he doesn't have [INAUDIBLE], [SPEAKING GERMAN], this, a nail, had something-- [SPEAKING GERMAN], that he passes.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He sees it's nice and clean, you know, pass.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when he passed by, he saw something's wrong.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He calls right away two guys, put him on the truck.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They put me-- they put me in-- in a-- in a [INAUDIBLE] [? die maker. ?] Half of this place was Polacks working-- all kinds of Polacks.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Half was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and-- and they put me in the milling machine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They give me the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The German-- the meister-- he was limping on a foot with a stick.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was walking with a cane.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When I came in, I heard screaming.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't know that this is here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What a [INAUDIBLE] this is.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you murdered wild men-- old men-- he didn't have teeth in the mouth.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But he was a-- an [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] He would eat a Jew up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And [LAUGHS] I stood this near machine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "A guy brought over the iron with the-- with the little wagon, you know, little thing, puts down-- puts down the-- the-- the-- the plan of what to do and walked away.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This is yours.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
